==English==

===Alternative spellings===
*[[czarist]], [[tzarist]]

===Noun===
'''tsarist'''
# one who supports a [[tsar]]

===Adjective===
'''tsarist'''
# expressing support for a [[tsar]]

===Dictionary notes=== [[Category:Dictionary notes]]
*'''American Heritage Dictionary''' (via answers.com) lists only “czarist”.
*'''Collins Word Exchange''' lists “tsarist” as an especially US variant of "czarist", but actually lacks an article on “czarist”. “Tzarist” is not mentioned at all.
*'''Merriam-Webster Online''' lists only “czarist”.
*'''MSN Encarta Dictionary''' lists all 3 spelling alternatives in the order: tsarist, csarist, tzarist.

